00:05:45.983 -- 00:05:48.112
gagal melindungi masyarakat.

00:05:48.174 -- 00:05:51.801
Pekan lalu,
bos sindikat kriminal besar Timur Tengah,

00:05:51.826 -- 00:05:53.403
bersama rekannya,

00:05:53.428 -- 00:05:55.911
tewas di bak sampah.

00:05:55.936 -- 00:05:56.666
TERIMA KASIH

00:05:56.739 -- 00:05:59.025
Pria itu? Wow.

