paham?

00:08:49.287 -- 00:08:50.497
- Ya.
- Siap, Bos.

00:08:51.019 -- 00:08:52.070
Ayo.

00:08:52.291 -- 00:08:54.211
Karena jika kalian diam...

00:08:56.822 -- 00:08:58.617
...aku harus bertindak.

00:09:02.165 -- 00:09:04.505
Aku harus bertindak...
bertindak...

00:09:04.588 -- 00:09:06.007
harus bertindak...

