orang di sekitar kita, kan?

00:13:23.294 -- 00:13:24.837
Kalian tidak paham?

00:13:25.672 -- 00:13:28.346
Baik. Dengarkan,
akan kujelaskan.

00:13:28.823 -- 00:13:30.009
Jika naik bus

00:13:30.034 -- 00:13:31.746
tanpa membayar tiket,

00:13:31.771 -- 00:13:33.810
jika ke bioskop,
atau mengambil pisang

00:13:33.835 -- 00:13:35.384
