00:47:27.687 -- 00:47:29.492
Tidak. Lakukan saja.

00:47:30.777 -- 00:47:32.865
Bagaimana proyek Grande Allee?

00:47:33.681 -- 00:47:35.986
Eh, serah terima teknis

00:47:36.011 -- 00:47:37.393
